      <Run FontFamily="times new roman" FontStyle="Italic" FontSize="14" Tag="__221">Note:</Run>
      <Run Tag="__221"> The 6&#x2013;10 average surplus is &#x201C;pumped up&#x201D; by the phenomenal success of #10 draft picks Paul Pierce, Jason Terry, Joe Johnson, and Caron Butler.</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Margin="0,1,0,0" TextAlignment="Justify" FontFamily="times new roman" FontSize="14">
